{"tid":1084991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警元朗掃淫窟大廈拉21人　包括3泰籍變性人","createTime":"2019-03-30T20:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T05:31:04.000Z","uid":136770,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d73db77eecaa1918619fda5548800823ec1b3ec","tid":1084991,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:17:41.000Z","msg":"元朗警區特別職務隊根據線報及深入調查後，昨日（30日）聯同新界北總區快速應變部隊、元朗警區雜項調查隊及特遣隊繼續進行一連串的掃黃行動。警員突擊搜查元朗壽富街一大廈，拘捕20名持護照的泰國籍男女，包括3名「人妖」及17女，1名持雙程證的內地女子，年齡介乎21至43歲，俱涉嫌違反逗留條件。 <br />\n<br />\n警方於行動中檢獲一批避孕套及潤滑劑。所有被捕男女現正被扣留調查。警方行動仍在進行，不排除有更多人被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n元朗警區一直非常關注並致力打擊區內非法賣淫活動。根據現行法例，「違反逗留條件」一經定罪，最高可被判處罰款5萬元及監禁2年；「為不道德目的而唆使他人」一經定罪，最高罰款1萬元及監禁6個月。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190331/photo/bkn-20190331002203509-0331_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190331032351\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190331%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190331002203509-0331_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190331032351&h=252ee358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有變性人呀仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班雞蟲屌咗男人都唔知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982b054cd657e1863faa262d00ed75d6e054edf3","tid":1084991,"uid":212246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T22:23:23.000Z","msg":"奇事　發覺這女郎 發覺這女郎 雙袋加一碌鋼"},{"pid":"08d8bdfc00a70ca44c8e0091de89a52caacaaeb7","tid":1084991,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"982b054cd657e1863faa262d00ed75d6e054edf3","tid":1084991,"uid":212246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T22:23:23.000Z","msg":"奇事　發覺這女郎 發覺這女郎 雙袋加一碌鋼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}